originalText.text: I only pick up cigars or water/ snacks!! These folks are well stocked. Fresh products and customer service is ALWAYS ON POINT!!! Neighborhood is a mixture between krazy kalm & dangerous! Get your grocery, mind your peas and Qs and all might be well!!! They make hot/cold sandwiches, but I do not know how any of these taste.

originalText.text: For the Last past few months, the prices has been changing on the dime without reason. Tonight was my last try, when I tried to bring up the difference in prices I was shut down by the guy working the front desk, with the "owner"  standing right behind me.   I have been going to this store for 10+ years and never had all mix-matched pricing happen.  To whoever sees this, know prices will change any were from $0.25- $1.00. Tonight the price is a hero, that was clearly printed for $4.99 ($5) was charged for $5.50. didn't really care about the money, just about the robbery.
